Project Name
Hackathon Team Formation Platform

Purpose
The purpose of this task is to detail the internal structure of the system components, including the back-end logic, database design, and front-end user interface components for the MVP.

System Components
The system is composed of three main components:

Back-End: Handles business logic and application rules.
Database: Stores all application data.
Front-End: Provides the user interface and user interaction.


Back-End: Key Classes
Class: User
Represents a hackathon participant.
Attributes:

userId
name
email
password
skills
preferredRole
experienceLevel
availabilityStatus

Methods:

register()
login()
updateProfile()
updateAvailability()


Class: Team
Represents a hackathon team.
Attributes:

teamId
teamName
description
requiredRoles
createdBy
members

Methods:

createTeam()
addMember()
removeMember()
viewTeamDetails()


Class: JoinRequest
Represents requests sent by users to join teams.
Attributes:

requestId
userId
teamId
status (pending / accepted / rejected)
requestDate

Methods:

sendRequest()
acceptRequest()
rejectRequest()


Class: IdeaLog
Supports the idea protection feature.
Attributes:

logId
teamId
ideaContent
createdBy
timestamp

Methods:

logIdea()
viewIdeaHistory()


Database Design (Document-Oriented – MongoDB)
Collection: users
{
  "userId": "string",
  "name": "string",
  "email": "string",
  "password": "string",
  "skills": ["string"],
  "preferredRole": "string",
  "experienceLevel": "string",
  "availabilityStatus": "boolean"
}
Mandatory fields: userId, email, password
Optional fields: skills, experienceLevel, availabilityStatus

Collection: teams
{
  "teamId": "string",
  "teamName": "string",
  "description": "string",
  "requiredRoles": ["string"],
  "createdBy": "userId",
  "members": ["userId"]
}

Collection: joinRequests
{
  "requestId": "string",
  "userId": "string",
  "teamId": "string",
  "status": "pending | accepted | rejected",
  "requestDate": "date"
}

Collection: ideaLogs
{
  "logId": "string",
  "teamId": "string",
  "ideaContent": "string",
  "createdBy": "userId",
  "timestamp": "date"
}

Entity Relationships (ERD – Text Description)

One user can create multiple teams
A user can send multiple join requests
A team can have multiple members
A team can have multiple idea logs


Front-End Components

Login and Registration pages
User Profile page
Team Creation page
Team Discovery page
Team Details page
Join Request management interface
Idea logging interface
